{"tid":258451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公平咩？女性首季收入增$800　男性無增長","createTime":"2017-05-26T06:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T04:17:42.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"058e029f1dc38eba97e5d64f11fee7d58ba0da06","tid":258451,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170526/photo/bkn-20170526141008667-0526_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170526143643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170526141008667-0526_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170526143643&h=bc1637d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涵蓋今年1至3月勞動人口、就業、失業及就業不足等統計數字的《綜合住戶統計調查按季統計報告》出爐。結果顯示，今年第一季的女性每月就業收入中位數比去年同期升800港元至12,800港元，但同期男士每月就業收入中位數卻原封不動，維持在1.8萬港元。而整體每月就業收入中位數無論是否計算農曆年花紅，則維持1.5萬港元，與上一季及去年第一季相同。<br />\n<br />\n今年首季香港就業人數逾382萬人，比去年第4季增加約3萬人，比去年同期亦升近4萬人，而就業不足率則比上季微跌0.3個百分點。月入方面，女性每月就業收入中位數包括花紅及不包括花紅分別為12,800港元及12,400港元，比去年首季分別增加800港元及400港元。"},{"pid":"1a02971d1b26316f16ed295e0510b3f6ad2945b3","tid":258451,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cab3c07b6a933767e784afcba4d8ee639a138ed","tid":258451,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"1q價錢"},{"pid":"5eda5bb14701686169c2df8f05e4a5b4393d4f18","tid":258451,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319bd6a33e12220a8dabada768143a4a08d3bbaa","tid":258451,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:51:24.000Z","msg":"計左ptgf?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6a63db784c496483f9aba1c23bba23c45d1586","tid":258451,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,